high_descs: Turn around and take one step, turn left, walk to the end of the couch and turn right for two steps.
Pick up the round, red object.
Turn around and take two steps, turn right for two steps, turn left for three steps, and then turn right to face the white table.
Put the round, red object down on the table, to the bottom left of the cardboard box.
Turn right and walk past the couch, turn right for one step and then left to face the bookcase.
Open the cabinet on the top shelf, take out the silver vase, and shut the door.
Turn left for one step, turn left for five steps and turn right to face the table.
Put the vase on the table near the chair on the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a red round object, a silver vase on the white table.

high_descs: turn around and walk straight a tiny bit then turn left and walk straight then turn left towards the shelf
pick up the red glass container on the shelf
turn around and walk straight towards the couch then turn right walk straight then turn left walk straight then turn right towards the table
put the red container down on the table
turn right and walk straight then turn right again and then turn left towards the shelf and look up
open the shelf door and remove the gray jar
turn left walk straight a tiny bit then turn left again and walk straight then turn right towards the table
put the gray jar down on the table next to the red container

high_descs: Turn to your right and go past the couch, to the white built in shelf's on the wall to your right.
Pick up the red vase on the right side of the second shelf from the bottom.
Turn to your left and go to the corner of the table closest to the couch.
Place the red vase on the table, in front of the front, right chair.
Turn to your right and go to the white cabinet above the shelf's, on the right.
Pull out the glass vase from the cabinet.
Turn to your left and go between the two chairs at the table that are closest to the couch.
Place the vase on the table, between the two chairs.
anns.task_desc: Put a two vases on the dining table.
